Cell["\<\
Now, UPPE still has an edge below 100 fs, but this is really only a factor 3 \
at best. At pulse durations above 1 ps, coupled wave eqns. are clearly \
superior. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9815522637217293`*^9, 
  3.9815523559746094`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3dc35825-fb7c-7640-93ad-\
2d4fc84f8131"]
},
